  "description": "<l>{<gold>{Entangle Oracle — Plant + Storm Druid}}\n\n<m>{<silver>{Physical Plant spells (Entangle + Thrashing Vines) made Overgrown by Thunderstorm (Storm), scaled by the Wildsurge Incantation keystone (+50% more to Storm & Plant spells). Cast on Critical auto-triggers Thunderstorm to keep plants watered.}}\n\n<m>{<red>{IMPORTANT / IMPORTANTE}}: This skeleton is built from VERIFIED sources (poe2db live, and a real poe.ninja Oracle PoB: poe.ninja/poe2/pob/1612e, checked 29 May 2026) — but two things are <red>{NOT fully verified}:\n1. <red>{Ascendancy ID 'Druid1'} is an <red>{[Inference]} — the canonical Oracle/Druid ID was not confirmed against repoe-fork/poe2. Verify before relying on it.\n2. <red>{The passive tree is NOT included} — the PoB decoder returned 0 allocated nodes, so node IDs could not be extracted. Allocate the tree in-game from the guide, or import the PoB into Path of Building 2 for the real tree.\n\n<grey>{Sources / Fuentes\n-------------------\n- Maxroll: maxroll.gg/poe2/build-guides/entangle-oracle-build-guide\n- Real PoB (lvl 94 Oracle, Entangle+Thrashing Vines+Thunderstorm): poe.ninja/poe2/pob/1612e\n- Skill data verified live on poe2db.tw (29 May 2026)}\n\n<grey>{Usage / Uso\n-------------------\n1. Drop into Documents/My Games/Path of Exile 2/BuildPlanner/\n2. Restart the client so the File Watcher picks it up\n3. This file carries the skill/support plan + gear-slot hints. Allocate the passive tree yourself (see the guide).}",
